   top-down platform and product family design
SO INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF PRODUCTION RESEARCH
LA English
DT Article
DE product development; product family design; modularity; commonality
ID MASS CUSTOMIZATION; LIFE-CYCLE; ARCHITECTURE; METHODOLOGY; PERFORMANCE;
