TI Impacts of common components on production system in an uncertain
   environment
SO SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH AND ESSAYS
LA English
DT Article
DE commonality; WITNESS; uncertainty
ID IMPERFECT PRODUCTION PROCESS; LEAD TIME UNCERTAINTY; QUALITY
